snippet.title: Manipulated Official Launch Trailer 2017
snippet.description:
Play on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/530510

Manipulated is a puzzle platformer designed to stretch your problem-solving abilities to the limit. This game is not easy, it’s full of intriguing puzzles and action-packed boss battles. Follow the story based on an actual experiment, try not to let the robots manipulate you!

Website: http://manipulatedgame.com
